---
// Premium full-bleed hero
---
<section style="position:relative;min-height:600px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;text-align:center;overflow:hidden;background:var(--cream);">
  <img src="/images/hero-bg.png" alt="" aria-hidden="true" style="position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;" />
  <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(246,230,212,.50),rgba(236,205,176,.42));"></div>
  <div class="pad-fluid" style="position:relative;padding:78px 44px;max-width:840px;width:100%;min-width:0;">
    <div style="display:inline-block;background:rgba(138,165,147,.22);color:var(--forest-mid);font-size:13px;font-weight:600;padding:7px 15px;border-radius:999px;margin-bottom:24px;line-height:1.4;">We find you the perfect therapist. Guaranteed.</div>
    <h1 class="h1-fluid" style="font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:500;font-size:64px;line-height:1.04;letter-spacing:-.02em;margin:0 auto 20px;max-width:760px;color:var(--forest-ink);">You're self-aware. Now<span style="color:var(--terracotta);font-style:italic;"><br>let's change something.</span></h1>
    <p style="font-size:19px;line-height:1.55;color:var(--taupe-3);margin:0 auto 30px;max-width:600px;">For the self-aware who are tired of insight that goes nowhere. Our founder personally matches you with a therapist she trained to do deeper work — hand-picked for you, not pulled from a directory.</p>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:13px;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:30px;">
      <a href="#book" class="btn btn-primary" style="text-decoration:none;background:var(--terracotta);color:var(--white);font-weight:600;font-size:16px;padding:16px 32px;border-radius:999px;box-shadow:0 16px 32px -14px rgba(33,58,48,.5);">Find my therapist →</a>
      <a href="#book" class="btn btn-soft" style="text-decoration:none;background:rgba(255,255,255,.85);color:var(--forest);font-weight:600;font-size:15.5px;padding:15px 26px;border-radius:999px;border:1px solid rgba(33,58,48,.14);display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;"><span style="width:9px;height:9px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--terracotta);"></span>Take the 60-second quiz</a>
    </div>
    <div style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;text-align:left;">
      <img src="/images/brooke-headshot.webp" alt="Brooke Sprowl, LCSW" style="width:54px;height:54px;border-radius:50%;object-fit:cover;flex:none;" />
      <div style="font-size:14px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.45;"><strong style="color:var(--ink);font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:600;font-size:16.5px;">Twenty years of clinical experience behind every match.</strong><br>Every therapist personally chosen by <strong style="font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:500;font-style:italic;color:var(--forest-ink);border-bottom:2px solid var(--terracotta);padding-bottom:2px;">Brooke Sprowl, LCSW</strong></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
